		<title>Afrisends says it is building what West Africa’s supply chains still lack</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/04/21/francophone-weekly-by-techcabal-019/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Lina Kacyem]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 21 Apr 2026 11:11:43 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Francophone Weekly]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Newsletters]]></category>
